The paper deals with the use of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for efficient data dissemination in wireless networks. This involves the use of algorithms based on neural networks to address issues related to QoS, capacity, and coverage. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of neural networks also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of UAVs for routing and relaying data suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
